{"tid":1933361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你食左人血饅頭未啊？（第一章-時間線）","createTime":"2020-03-19T08:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T08:14:05.000Z","uid":352673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9044b5be2cea50bc4ce42dd77f8ab219b61bbd4c","tid":1933361,"uid":352673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"時間線<br />\r\n2月22日<br />\r\n重現社區第一次街站@黃大仙<br />\r\n當時為譚得志的街站，重現社區只是合辦<br />\r\n快必在街站結束後捐贈6桶漂白水予重現社區的主辦方，啊Joe<br />\r\n並且幫啊Joe call gogovan並替他支付車費<br />\r\n。<br />\r\n2月27日<br />\r\n重現社區第二次街站@佐敦偉晴街<br />\r\n重現社區為主辦方，並邀請了當區區議員出席<br />\r\n是次街站獲得了兩箱搓手液<br />\r\n街站後有小型飯局，費用為零。<br />\r\n。<br />\r\n3月5日<br />\r\n重現社區第三次街站@深水埗鴨寮街<br />\r\n重現社區為主辦方，並邀請了當區區議員出席<br />\r\n是次街站並沒有特別收獲。<br />\r\n。<br />\r\n3月7日<br />\r\n重現社區第四次街站@鑽石山龍蟠苑<br />\r\n重現社區為主辦方，並邀請了黃大仙大坊小會合辦<br />\r\n是次街站並沒有特別收獲。<br />\r\n。<br />\r\n3月19日<br />\r\n重現社區第五次街站@彩禧路公園<br />\r\n重現社區為主辦方<br />\r\n未知有否收獲。<br />\r\n。"},{"pid":"3d6f1449b2c6c6908a481d9c8017b553c0e8421f","tid":1933361,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"34b37b0006cb0b2a3ab51204630ae59031e1b7a1","tid":1933361,"uid":352673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"第二篇-證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJxfpNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJxfpNw.png&h=7b24c4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYNZRsA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYNZRsA.png&h=d450385b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgPtKNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgPtKNL.png&h=e17ee7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pua8KNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpua8KNT.png&h=e5af93d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家可以去睇下。呢啲就係我地第一篇提及過嘅酒精搓手液事件。<br />\n我地偉大嘅Joe哥將呢兩箱酒精搓手液拎翻彩雲賣<br />\n係$20/1